ZH: 宁愿吃素也不吃肉。
EN: I'd rather be vegetarian than eat meat.
ZH: 宁愿一个人待在家里也不愿意去参加派对。
EN: I'd rather stay home alone than go to a party.
ZH: 他宁愿辞职也不愿意继续在这家公司工作。
EN: He'd rather quit than continue working at this company.
ZH: 我宁愿在家自学也不喜欢上学校。
EN: I prefer self-studying at home than going to school.
ZH: 我宁愿等一会儿也不想赶火车错过了。
EN: I'd rather wait a bit than miss the train.
ZH: 她宁愿每天坚持锻炼也不愿意胖起来。
EN: She'd rather exercise every day than gain weight.
ZH: 宁愿失去一切也不愿意牺牲我的原则。
EN: I'd rather lose everything than sacrifice my principles.
ZH: 我宁愿和你坦诚相待，不愿隐瞒任何事情。
EN: I prefer to be honest with you and not conceal anything.
ZH: 宁愿迟到也不想匆忙准备。
EN: I'd rather be late than prepare in a rush.
ZH: 我宁愿工作到深夜也不愿意拖延任务的完成。
EN: I'd rather work late into the night than procrastinate completing the tasks.
ZH: 宁愿过清贫的日子也不愿陷入债务之中。
EN: I'd rather live a frugal life than get into debt.
ZH: 我宁愿走路到那里也不想坐公共汽车。
EN: I'd rather walk there than take the bus.
ZH: 宁愿错过一次机会也不愿意被迫做一件不喜欢的事情。
EN: I'd rather miss an opportunity than be forced to do something I don't like.
ZH: 我宁愿每天吃相同的食物也不想下厨。
EN: I'd rather eat the same food every day than cook.
ZH: 宁愿失去爱情也不愿失去自由。
EN: I'd rather lose love than lose freedom.
ZH: 我宁愿相信别人的好也不愿意怀疑他们的意图。
EN: I'd rather believe in others' goodness than suspect their intentions.
ZH: 宁愿花点时间理解，也不愿意轻易下结论。
EN: I'd rather take some time to understand than jump to conclusions.
ZH: 我宁愿节省开支也不愿意为名牌奢侈品买单。
EN: I'd rather cut expenses than pay for luxury brand items.
ZH: 宁愿房子小点也不愿意离城市远。
EN: I'd rather have a smaller house than live far from the city.
ZH: 我宁愿让他们不高兴也不愿意妥协我的原则。
EN: I'd rather make them unhappy than compromise my principles.
